{
  "id": "6a37abd5db1401d0061f0491",
  "title": "練りものにハマってる",
  "created": 1782033366,
  "updated": 1782033370,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6a37abd5db1401d0061f0491",
      "text": "練りものにハマってる",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1782033366,
      "updated": 1782033366
    },
    {
      "id": "6a37abd50000000000d7926d",
      "text": "from [2026/06/18]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1782033366,
      "updated": 1782033366
    },
    {
      "id": "6a37abd70000000000d7927f",
      "text": "[mtane0412.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1782033367,
      "updated": 1782033368
    },
    {
      "id": "6a37abd50000000000d7926e",
      "text": " [練りもの]にハマってる",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1782033366,
      "updated": 1782033370
    },
    {
      "id": "6a37abd50000000000d7926f",
      "text": "  猫がすごい欲しがるので悩む",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1782033366,
      "updated": 1782033370
    },
    {
      "id": "6a37abd50000000000d79270",
      "text": "  塩分が高いので上げない方がいいはず",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1782033366,
      "updated": 1782033370
    },
    {
      "id": "6a37abd50000000000d79271",
      "text": "  練り物は美味しく優秀[zatsma.icon][joniel.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1782033366,
      "updated": 1782033370
    },
    {
      "id": "6a37abd50000000000d79272",
      "text": "   朝時間がないときにちくわ単品を頬張ることがある",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1782033366,
      "updated": 1782033370
    },
    {
      "id": "6a37abd50000000000d79273",
      "text": "    [時間がないときの朝食]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1782033366,
      "updated": 1782033370
    },
    {
      "id": "6a37abd50000000000d79274",
      "text": "   猫のおやつには[黒はんぺん]など良いのでは……と素人ながら思ったが、東海エリア外での入手性が低く残念",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1782033366,
      "updated": 1782033370
    },
    {
      "id": "6a37abd50000000000d79275",
      "text": "    おいしそう[mtane0412.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1782033366,
      "updated": 1782033370
    },
    {
      "id": "6a37abd50000000000d79276",
      "text": "  加工食品を食べるときにもし宇宙人が人類を家畜化して美味しく加工して食べ始めたら...みたいなことを考える[mtane0412.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1782033366,
      "updated": 1782033370
    },
    {
      "id": "6a37abd50000000000d79277",
      "text": "   練りものは相当エグい",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1782033366,
      "updated": 1782033370
    },
    {
      "id": "6a37abd50000000000d79278",
      "text": "   \t+1[sta.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1782033366,
      "updated": 1782033370
    },
    {
      "id": "6a37abd50000000000d79279",
      "text": "   \t[キメラアント編]を思い出した[! [terang.icon]]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1782033366,
      "updated": 1782033370
    },
    {
      "id": "6a37abd50000000000d7927a",
      "text": "   成分表には魚肉としか書かれていなくてスケトウダラなのかなんなのかもわからない",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1782033366,
      "updated": 1782033370
    },
    {
      "id": "6a37abd50000000000d7927b",
      "text": "  手作り[かまぼこ]が滅茶苦茶美味いという会話を思い出した[hoagecko.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1782033366,
      "updated": 1782033370
    },
    {
      "id": "6a37abd50000000000d7927c",
      "text": "  \tこんなこと書いたらかまぼこが食べたくなっちゃった",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1782033366,
      "updated": 1782033370
    },
    {
      "id": "6a37abd50000000000d7927d",
      "text": "  \tたべたくなっちゃった[caki.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1782033366,
      "updated": 1782033370
    },
    {
      "id": "6a37abd50000000000d7927e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1782033366,
      "updated": 1782033366
    }
  ]
}